Venue: CCXT, IB, FTX, etc.
PositionStatus: OPENED, CLOSED, CLOSING
AccountStatus: READY, ACTIVE, CLOSING

IMPORTANT: Always import from nautilus_trader
Never use strings
Always use module.ENUM format

Example: order = MarketOrder(..., order_side=OrderSide.BUY)
NOT: order = MarketOrder(..., order_side="BUY")

Docs: https://nautilustrader.io/docs/latest/api/enums/
"""

